      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really nice shape, super clean inside, and runs like an absolute dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and is just waiting for someone new to take it out on the road. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend trip, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I do!",
