    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 3.4L flat-six features Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, delivering a linear torque curve and exceptional throttle response. The mid-engine architecture ensures a low polar moment of inertia, further enhanced by a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a communicative hydraulic steering rack. Recent preventive maintenance includes a full cooling system refresh and updated suspension bushings to maintain chassis rigidity. While displaying minor aesthetic patina consistent with spirited road use, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain superb, offering a tactile driving experience that modern EPS systems cannot replicate.",
